{"tid":1670113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[加泰]仲記唔記得咩叫兄弟爬山？咩叫核爆不割？唔好俾對家藉呢件事分化好嗎？","createTime":"2019-10-23T01:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T01:48:41.000Z","uid":66260,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb2206840a6f29a806811044dd1411845115c3e","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山係用各自既方法去達到目的<br />\n你呢邊集會求耶穌打救，個邊求黃大仙打救都得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你認同connect加泰咪去囉，唔認同咪唔好理囉</span><br />\n<br />\n核爆不割係指你唔認同對方做法都要支持同幫佢解釋<br />\n你估謝sir同er er sir對住班毅進仔唔想屌佢地老母咩？咪日日4點鐘幫佢死兜爛兜。你地唔係連黑警都不如下話？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得connect加泰有問題，咪幫佢地解釋幫佢地spin囉。twitter攻勢、英文西班牙文連儂牆、外國手足、登報，我地咁疊馬唔係做唔到呀嘛？</span><br />\n<br />\n我好肯定對家一定會煲大單集會屈你乜乜柒柒。既然避唔到咁就唔好避，我就唔信靠手足既文宣攻勢唔可以死都拗返生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1d8b0619f4fdcce5b80585c4bcd0a6851f8213","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37415baa781c6e85ae659b8239675c7c1e694e90","tid":1670113,"uid":219256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:37:54.000Z","msg":"不如講下點解加泰集會是有問題 一黎有人影到佢地有人高舉共產旗 很多香港人到底清唔清楚 我地的行為目的 <br />\ntwitter攻勢 &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;講了4個月 有幾多人做過 200萬人連10%都沒人去玩<br />\n有時間 不如CONNECT 議員支持法案先 香港成個世界得美國佬做到野<br />\n你R加泰 &lt; 但要清楚你要做咩先 係反警暴 OK?"},{"pid":"67b2b16cd4ebc882c7d18423a171597c52b43905","tid":1670113,"uid":328969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:40:24.000Z","msg":"明知對面會屈你，點解唔盡量搞個冇咁大爭議，比較多人認同的「反全球警暴」？<br />\n你知唔知解釋同spin有幾難?人吔係用緊國家機器，文宣得自己一對手屌你老母"},{"pid":"208e646a59e2cb0a9398bfa3c6139122854c5664","tid":1670113,"uid":65074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"加泰post全部變晒罵戰<br />\n我都相信真係有手足有心想支持  <br />\n但由結果黎睇   只係引起分化<br />\n<br />\n加泰post一律冷處理"},{"pid":"1c2a7c61978c464f16828631c7f20673a85b6610","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e03f33059faf3e85db0da8bc4580533adf97468","tid":1670113,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:29:26.000Z","msg":"推呢個！！"},{"pid":"7d3038f4156bab7ea022ac7bee75f6d5f910daf3","tid":1670113,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔去加泰？<br />\n去英領！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【上議辯論造勢大會】<br />\n10月23日（三）<br />\n英國領事館門口<br />\n19：30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5iHJGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5iHJGT.jpg&h=30a60c49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd8bc6f9e359d5d1f673d2c735be82085dd71bae","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5ca11e51e1dea2e12bc484a4655dcddb46c3b7","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"12點後唔講<br />\n推埋呢次"},{"pid":"85efa0f13698c4647106c627726bce391d6f3a95","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"2點後繼續講<br />\n再推"},{"pid":"7f45a3af799ba31e7b9679821d745b4ac0074f1f","tid":1670113,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61773e405f19c7413aeaa4f430b3503383a23ef3","tid":1670113,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07961ef3b902dac637879560a3b01bb54b634e19","tid":1670113,"uid":66260